data.name: grdList.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.SG_CODE , A.GROUP_GUBUN , A.SG_NAME , A.SG_NAME_KANA , A.SG_YMD , A.SUGA_CHANGE , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('SUGA_CHANGE',A.SUGA_CHANGE) SUGA_CHANGE_NM_D , A.BULYONG_YMD , A.BULYONG_SAYU , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('BULYONG_SAYU',A.BULYONG_SAYU) BULYONG_SAYU_NM_D , DECODE(A.DANUI, '000', '', A.DANUI) DANUI , FN_OCS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('ORD_DANUI', A.DANUI) DANUI_NAME , A.BUN_CODE , FN_BAS_LOAD_BUN_NAME_NEW(A.BUN_CODE, A.SG_YMD) BUN_CODE_NAME , A.MARUME_GUBUN , A.SG_UNION , A.REMARK , FN_BAS_LOAD_CODE_NAME('POGWAL_GUBUN',A.MARUME_GUBUN) MARUME_NAME , A.HUBAL_DRG_YN , A.SUNAB_QCODE_OUT , A.SUNAB_QCODE_INP , A.TAX_YN FROM BAS0310 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.SG_NAME_IND LIKE :f_sg_code AND A.BUN_CODE LIKE :f_bun_code || '%' AND A.SG_YMD = ( SELECT MAX(Z.SG_YMD) FROM BAS0310 Z WHERE Z.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND Z.SG_CODE = A.SG_CODE ) ORDER BY A.SG_CODE
